The '''Simbelmyne Calendar 1998''' features 13 black and white illustrations by [[Karolina Stopa]] and [[Arkadiusz Kubala]]. Gregorian calendar compared with the reckonings of [[Reckoning of Rivendell|Imladris]], [[Buckland]], [[Gondor]] and the [[Dwarves]]. Moon phases are displayed. From the [[Polish Tolkien Society]]. 

* Dimensions: 8 3/8 x 11 5/8 inches
* Clear plastic cover; stapled
